# US English Dashboard Copy

- Write all user-facing dashboard text in US English.
- Prefer concise, natural labels used in apps (for example: "Last updated", not "Last render").
- Use US date/locale formatting for UI timestamps unless a task explicitly requests another locale.
- Keep weather and agenda labels in English, including accessibility labels (`aria-label`).

## Examples

- Good: `Last updated`, `Weather`, `Today`, `Status icons`
- Avoid: `Laatste render`, `Weer`, `Vandaag`, `Status iconen`
